    "created_at": "2014-08-15T22:54:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-08-15T22:54:20Z",
    "body": "Is there a particular reason that you singled out slice iterators rather than all iterators? I would expect that an empty iterator could be easily constructed through `None::<T>.iter()`, but it doesn't allow for interoperability with other slice iterators (when stored in structures).\n",
